FBIS3-12357 "drnes039_n_94008" FBIS-NES-94-039 Document Type:Daily Report 28 Feb 1994 LEBANON President, Others Comment on Church Bombing Speaker Urges Vigilance NC2702145894 Beirut Radio Lebanon in Arabic 1135 GMT 27 Feb 94 NC2702145894 Beirut Radio Lebanon Language: Arabic Article Type:BFN [Text] Chamber of Deputies Speaker Nabih Birri has stated that the purpose of this abominable crime against worshipers in Sayyidat al-Najat Church was to sabotage general stability in Lebanon. He said this crime, which coincided with an Israeli escalation in southern Lebanon, is an attempt to divert world attention from the Ibrahimi Mosque massacre. He noted that Israel is behind all this. Speaker Birri called on the Lebanese to be vigilant and responsible so that we will all emerge from this test with more faith in Lebanon.
